Description: With the Google People API you can read and manage the authenticated user's Contacts, read and copy the authenticated user's "other contacts", read profile information for authenticated users and their contacts, and read domain profiles and contacts.
Name: Google Contacts

Methods.Name: Get Person
Methods.Description: Returns information about the specified person.

Methods.Name: List New And Updated People
Methods.Description: Returns a list of the authenticated user's contacts created or updated since the last time this action was executed.

Methods.Name: List People
Methods.Description: Returns a list of the authenticated user's contacts.
